com.pega.pegarules.pub.session.url

Interface PegaURLBuilder.IApplicationAliasComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PegaURLBuilder.IBuilder
    Enclosing interface:
    PegaURLBuilder

    public static interface PegaURLBuilder.IApplicationAliasComponent
extends PegaURLBuilder.IBuilder
    PegaURLBuilder.IApplicationAliasComponent is used to construct application alias part in the complete Pega URL.

    Refer PegaURLBuilder for constructing Pega URLs.

    This class is used to construct bold component in Pega URL as shown below:
    http://{hostname}:{port}/prweb/{ServletName}/app/{ApplicationAlias}_1234/{Access Group Hash}/{Thread Name or Static content directory}/

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      PegaURLBuilder.IAccessGroupComponent currentApplication()
      Adds application alias component to URL deriving it from current logged in application.
      For example this method adds app/TestApp1 to URL if TestApp1 is the application alias for the current logged in application.
      PegaURLBuilder.IAccessGroupComponent currentApplicationWithUniqueId()
      Adds application alias component deriving it from current logged in application and also appends unique identifier.

    • Method Detail

      • withApplication

        PegaURLBuilder.IAccessGroupComponent withApplication(java.lang.String applicationName,
                                                     java.lang.String applicationVersion)
        Adds application alias component to URL from given application name and version. This need not be the current logged in application.
        For example this method adds app/TestApp1 to URL if TestApp1 is the application alias for the given applicationName and applicationVersion.
        Parameters:
        applicationName - Application Name to find relevant application alias.
        applicationVersion - Application Version to find relevant application alias.
        Returns:
        PegaURLBuilder.IAccessGroupComponent An instance to build Access Group Hash.

      • currentApplication

        PegaURLBuilder.IAccessGroupComponent An instance to build Access Group Hash

      • currentApplicationWithUniqueId

        PegaURLBuilder.IAccessGroupComponent currentApplicationWithUniqueId()
        Adds application alias component deriving it from current logged in application and also appends unique identifier. This is used in mashup URLs to have unique sessions.
        For example,this method adds app/TestApp1_1275 to URL if TestApp1 is the application alias for the current application and 1275 is a generated unique Identifier for unique sessions.
        Returns:
        PegaURLBuilder.IAccessGroupComponent An instance to build Access Group Hash.
